snippet.title: C-VINE News Network OFFICIAL
snippet.description:
We the People Are the News Now!

This grass roots Breaking News movement owned by the people, has exploded in popularity.

All news is provided with source and vetted before release from our Citizen Journalists.

ALL are volunteers.

Everything placed in a Charitable Trust.

The only things not allowed in our home are disruptive trouble  makers or trolls. We run a tight ship.

"We the People" are C-VINE!

C-VINE.COM
